full_threads.body:
Hi Heath,


There are a few tweaks we need on the RR LifeWorks website. Please review the below carefully. It's a lot of text as I have listed the changes per page - most of it is just formatting/ spacing and ensuring everything is consistently centre aligned.


Any questions, let me know. Thanks!

  • News posts and client stories. When we click on these pages, we lose the menu bar and the footer. Can we please re-format these so that the main menu bar and footer can be seen when clicking on the individual news posts and client stories?

On mobile:
  • Case Management page: large space between "Benefits" headline and the benefits icons. Can we compress this? For the "Contact Us", "Meet our team", "Receive your program", "Start your program" icons, can we move them in the middle.
  • Dietetics page: In the "our team can provide" dotpoints spacing issues with text. Can we please clean this up? Can we also reduce the space between the "Dietitians' input would benefit you in many ways such as:" and the icons/ benefits underneath it? Cooking image is aligned to the left side can we please centre this? For the "Contact Us", "Meet our team", "Receive your program", "Start your program" icons, can we move them in the middle.
  • Occupational therapy: Can we also reduce the space between the "Benefits of occupational therapy" and the icons/ benefits underneath it? For the "Contact Us", "Meet our team", "Receive your program", "Start your program" icons, can we move them in the middle. Cooking image is aligned to the left side can we please centre this?
  • Physiotherapy page: Can we also reduce the space between the "Benefits of physiotherapy" and the icons/ benefits underneath it? Can we centre the image of the lady helping the man with the weights? Can we centre align the text for "Achieve your goals" and the body text underneath? For the "Contact Us", "Meet our team", "Receive your program", "Start your program" icons, can we move them in the middle. Cooking image is aligned to the left side can we please centre this?
  • Social work page: Can we centre align the intro body text? Can we also reduce the space between the "Benefits" and the icons/ benefits underneath it? Can we centre align the "Achieve your goals" text? Can we centre align the image of the man having coffee with a social worker? Can we centre align the text for "Achieve your goals" and the body text underneath? For the "Contact Us", "Meet our team", "Receive your program", "Start your program" icons, can we move them in the middle.
  • Speech pathology page: Can we centre align the intro body text? Can we also reduce the space between the "Benefits of speech pathology" and the icons/ benefits underneath it? Can we centre align the image of the lady and man in the garden? Can we centre align the text for "Achieve your goals"? For the "Contact Us", "Meet our team", "Receive your program", "Start your program" icons, can we move them in the middle.
  • For the overall therapies & supports page can we align the icons for "Contact Us", "Meet our team", "Receive your program", "Start your program"?
  • For the overall programs and services page can we align the icons for "Contact Us", "Meet our team", "Receive your program", "Start your program"? Can we also reduce the space between "I'm interested. What do I need to do?"
  • Recreational Therapy Sydney: Centre align all text. Centre align all icons.
  • Driving Assessment: Centre align all text. Centre align all icons. Reduce space between "What we offer" and dotpoints underneath. Centre align all icons.
  • Home modifications and equipment scripting: Centre align all text. Centre align all icons. Reduce space between "What we offer" and the text underneath it.
  • Horticultural therapy: Centre align all text. Centre align all icons.
  • Hydrotherapy: Centre align all text. Centre align all icons. Reduce space between "I'm interested. What do I need to do?" and the icons underneath.
  • Mobility Programs: Centre align all text. Centre align all icons. Reduce space between "I'm interested. What do I need to do?" and the icons underneath.
  • Seating assessment: Centre align all text. Centre align all icons. Reduce space between "I'm interested. What do I need to do?" and the icons underneath.
  • Upper limb therapy program: Centre align all text. Centre align all icons.
  • Reduce space between "I'm interested. What do I need to do?" and the icons underneath.
  • Technology page: Centre align all icons.
  • Armeo Power: Centre align all text. Funding page needs to align to the programs/ services and therapies pages (please review funding in mobile). Centre align all icons.
  • C-MillVR+: Centre align all text. Funding page needs to align to the programs/ services and therapies pages (please review funding in mobile). Centre align all icons.
  • DIEGO: Centre align all text. Funding page needs to align to the programs/ services and therapies pages (please review funding in mobile). Centre align all icons.
  • EksoNR: Centre align all text. Funding page needs to align to the programs/ services and therapies pages (please review funding in mobile). Centre align all icons.
  • Lokomat: Centre align all text. Funding page needs to align to the programs/ services and therapies pages (please review funding in mobile). Centre align all icons.
  • Zero G: Lokomat: Centre align all text. Funding page needs to align to the programs/ services and therapies pages (please review funding in mobile). Centre align all icons.

Also, when we scroll on mobile, we cannot reach the bottom pages under Programs/ Services and Technology such as Zero G page and the Upper Limb program page.

Can we amend this please?

Thanks Heath,
Janina
